                                                    img.img-responsive.media-object.center-block(src="images/icon_money.png", alt="Icon Money")
                                            .media-body
                                                h4.media-heading.icon-subheader Low Cost
                                                p Employing staff through Catapult is hardly more expensive than employing staff directly. You pay just 10% extra, but we do all the paperwork.
                                                p A Catapult member of staff working a 7 hour shift at £7.20/ hour would cost you £58.25 directly including tax & NI, or £64.07 through Catapult.

