                                                    img.img-responsive.media-object.center-block(src="images/icon_timesheet.png", alt="Icon Timesheet")
                                            .media-body
                                                h4.media-heading.icon-subheader Transparent
                                                p No hidden fees, you pay just 10% on hours worked. You don't pay anything until you've confirmed a shift was performed to your satisfaction.
                                                p It's a true meritocracy, see how staff have been rated by other employers like you. Rate our staff when you approve timesheets.

                                    .col-md-5.col-md-offset-2
                                        .media
