                                                a(href='#')
                                                    img.img-responsive.media-object.center-block(src="images/icon_watch.png", alt="Icon Watch")
                                            .media-body
                                                h4.media-heading.icon-subheader 24/7
                                                p Most of our offers are fulfilled within an hour, get quick confirmation whether it's last minute bookings or planning ahead for busy days.
                                                p Unlike traditional staffing agencies, Catapult is available to book the staff you need 24/7.

                                .row
