                                                a(href='#')
                                                    img.img-responsive.media-object.center-block(src="images/icon_device.png", alt="Icon Device")
                                            .media-body
                                                h4.media-heading.icon-subheader Fast, Simple & Easy
                                                p Making a booking with Catapult takes just a few minutes. If you want to to re-book the same staff for another day, it takes just seconds.
                                                p Get instant confirmation when your offer is accepted by somebody, so you're certain who is arriving and when.

                                    .col-md-5.col-md-offset-2
